item.title: HELP How do i remove this
item.dc:creator: @darkageisme darkageisme
item.description:
@darkageisme wrote:

[quote=“Christmas_tree, post:2, topic:478093”]Please refrain from making multiple topics as this is agains Global and Sectional rules.

What revision are you working with? What base?

Either way, it’s probably only sending the interface when you’re in a certain zone. Try searching for the text within your client class (or it may be a different class depending on your server base) and you will find it will be sending when you are within a certain area. You will need to change the coordinates of these areas to suit your needs.[/quote]
